cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or data, please cite it as below."
title: >-
  The fate of the Sm fold under genome reduction: a structure-informed
  phylogeny across the three domains of life
abstract: >-
  Analysis code and derived data for an integrated study of the Sm/Lsm/Hfq
  superfamily: a structure-guided three-domain phylogeny, a dual-method
  bacterial Hfq phylogeny, a completeness-controlled census of Hfq loss across
  bacterial lifestyles, and a structurally-verified census of Sm-fold retention
  in DPANN/Asgard archaea versus loss in the bacterial CPR radiation.
type: software
authors:
